channel.description:
This was originally made by defyboy, i'm just adding and changing a few things around.
[ul][li]Added Old Engine Sprite Dump[/li] [li]Added Better Renaming Method[/li][/ul]
Next Update will include:
[ul][li]Renaming of new cache files[/li] [li]Renaming error recording (i added this in my version when i started renaming the new cache and it couldnt find names for hundreds of files it was outputting too much)[/li][/ul]
[br][size=1]Posted on: March 10, 2007, 02:39:40 AM[/size][hr]oh by the way this is compiled in java 6 so if your getting a class version error that is why :p
